Tadiaľto.

329
00:30:42,837 --> 00:30:45,280
Som v poriadku. Choďte bezo mňa.

330
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,555
Choď, Jin Soo.

331
00:31:08,998 --> 00:31:10,325
Poručíčka Oh!

332
00:31:11,990 --> 00:31:13,209
Tadiaľto.

333
00:32:28,659 --> 00:32:29,872
Nie.

334
00:32:39,007 --> 00:32:41,149
Poďme. Poďme.

335
00:32:56,208 --> 00:32:57,792
Poďme tadiaľto.

336
00:33:00,036 --> 00:33:01,275
Opatrne.

337
00:33:20,989 --> 00:33:24,109
Odstúp od toho dievčaťa.

338
00:33:24,109 --> 00:33:25,593
Jin Soo.

339
00:33:27,690 --> 00:33:30,882
To je v poriadku. Poslúchnime ho.

340
00:33:32,833 --> 00:33:34,011
Založ si putá.

341
00:33:37,172 --> 00:33:40,001
Prosím, neublížte Sun Young.

342
00:33:40,001 --> 00:33:42,082
Už to viac nebudem opakovať.
Založ si putá.

343
00:33:58,650 --> 00:34:00,260
- Poručíčka Oh.
- Poručíčka Oh!

344
00:34:01,711 --> 00:34:03,000
Si v poriadku?

345
00:34:04,636 --> 00:34:06,476
Som v poriadku.

346
00:34:06,476 --> 00:34:09,875
Som v poriadku. Utekajte nájsť deti.

347
00:34:09,875 --> 00:34:11,352
Odišli tadiaľto.

348
00:34:11,352 --> 00:34:12,902
Zostaňte s poručíčkou Oh.

349
00:34:12,902 --> 00:34:14,156
Dávajte si pozor.

350
00:34:17,047 --> 00:34:18,390
Si v poriadku?

351
00:34:25,326 --> 00:34:26,944
Krič o pomoc.

352
00:34:28,301 --> 00:34:29,571
Čo?

353
00:34:29,571 --> 00:34:32,553
Krič o pomoc tak hlasno, ako môžeš.

354
00:34:35,060 --> 00:34:36,353
Pomôžte mi.

355
00:34:36,353 --> 00:34:37,509
Hlasnejšie.

356
